title: Video Container Batch Remuxer (FFMPEG+SCRIPT)
description:
FFMPEG Batch Conversion scrips for any file format

It'll help you convert an entire folder from one format to the other with LOSSY codecs, by correctly changing the container format with FFMPEG. All automated all you have to do is double click the file. 

Instructions: Place ffmpeg.exe along with what ever .bat file you need. Rather you need mkv to mp4, or mp4 to mkv, place them in the folder with your videos. Double click the bat file, and it'll do the rest
